events.name: エントランスへの移動場所
フォティゾナ王宮2F_Fに移動

parameters:
Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'This is so boring! I went to look
for General Atu, but I have no idea where he is...'
Goat of the Bulk Gang: It's you guys! I'm glad you're safe!
Priestess Sophia: Why are you deeper inside than us...?

Goat of the Bulk Gang: I broke through the wall and came in!
Hahaha, this kind of thing is a piece of cake on the
battlefield.
Clea: That blow earlier was impressive.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: I'm really grateful to you guys for
rescuing me, who had the potential to become the same as
that thing.

Priestess Sophia: If that's the case, please come with us.
If Rex-sama's castle is destroyed any further, it will be
unbearable!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Alright, I understand. I will follow
the benefactors of the Bulk Gang!

\CL Sophia has \C[14]unlocked the support skill True Goat
Strike \C[0]and can now use it\|.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Guild. A merchant who is cooperating with the Guild Leader
said, 'I was asked by the Guild Leader and ended up coming
all the way here...'

Guild. A merchant who is cooperating with the Guild said,
'I'm running a shop exclusively for Guild members here.'

Guild. A merchant who is cooperating with the Guild said, 'I
owe that person a debt... and now is the time for me to
repay it.'

Guild. The merchant who is cooperating with the Guild said,
'...I'll definitely charge you for my services.'

Guild. The merchant who is cooperating with the Guild said,
Yes, I'll give this to you as well.

Guild. The merchant who is cooperating with the Guild said,
'This is a family heirloom that has been passed down in our
clan, which has been engaged in trade for a long time.'

Guild. The merchant who is cooperating with the Guild said,
Please use it carefully.

Guild. The merchant who is cooperating with the Guild said,
'And please, help me seek revenge against the Empire... for
my one and only son--'

Guild. I'm sorry, but I've been instructed by the guild
leader to receive proper compensation for assisting Ftera...

Guild. The merchant who is assisting Ftera says, 'I can't
help but respect him for thinking about what will happen
after this battle is over... I can't help but look up to
him.'

Guild. The merchant who is assisting Ftera says, 'If you
need anything, please come back anytime.'

Guild. The merchant who is assisting Ftera says, 'Since that
day... I have been running around the country, preparing a
lot of inventory for today, for this day.'

Guild. A merchant who is cooperating with Ftera says, 'If
you need anything, please come back anytime.'
